name: CoreAPI Connectivity_APIClient
description: API to access the Planet 9 API Client responses
about:
Description

Planet 9 "API Client" maintains the list of all API's and enables you to test the "API Designer" API's.

The "API_Connectivity_API Client" API provides your app the ability to verify your API responses. Using this API you can perform the "GET" and "LIST" operation on the API Client.


Operations Performed 

List

As a response for "List" operation you will the list of all API's and API groups available in Planet 9 system.

ResponseList - Definition

Get

Get the API details corresponding to the API Client ID
